{"tid":2368200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌：佐敦及油麻地一帶有禁足令效果會更好","createTime":"2021-01-16T03:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T07:02:48.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"42b39379fbb72871f00dfd5e52eccc066fc14687","tid":2368200,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:36:33.000Z","msg":"許樹昌：佐敦及油麻地一帶強制檢測如有禁足令效果會更好 <br />\n中大醫學院內科及藥物治療學系系主任許樹昌指，如果可以囊括所有受疫情影響的大廈，相信是足夠，呼籲有關樓宇的住客盡快接受檢測，否則難以控制疫情。他又指當區不少劏房，沒有住客名單，難以追蹤居民有否做檢測，建議設立流動採樣車，方便居民深夜都可以做檢測，又指如果配合禁足令效果會更好。 <br />\n<br />\n港大醫學院助理院長孔繁毅認為，目前做法已經足夠，指若要規定整個社區無個案都要強制檢測並不可行，又認為最重要是檢測在48至72小時內有結果，以便追蹤第2至第3層的接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2375043\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2375043&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=fd4929a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2375043</a>"},{"pid":"985ce8c52792c8b3e85114bdaa8f97a9a9cd1d12","tid":2368200,"uid":93600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"cb35f1edb4248b7e64fe850be59ab54261c301a1","tid":2368200,"uid":14261,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b0097c3f3a0c938a84af1943e83719698bc27d","tid":2368200,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ed2283273ae8b39728a3324c7df83b6fffc3db","tid":2368200,"uid":343050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"64355e37c26cf72f52a12172ebe755a3b00d59dd","tid":2368200,"uid":39871,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:37:50.000Z","msg":"老闆: 好啊 咁我即刻叫油尖旺同事返工先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6f79cdc0c945d6da8da600e05be33955c0e09d","tid":2368200,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:38:09.000Z","msg":"政府疫苗顧問專家委員會成員許樹昌指，BioNTech疫苗已提交所有數據，可能會最先獲安排接種，政府訂購的700多萬劑將分6次來港，每次約100萬。他指香港的確診個案不及歐美國家多，因此不會效法部分海外國家做法，為了提高疫苗接種率而延後第二劑接種時間，避免影響疫苗效力。他指BioNTech疫苗需要在負70度以下儲存，稀釋後6小時內要接種，建議活動能力高的長者可以到社區會堂接種，政府亦可以上門為院舍長者接種。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2375032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2375032&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=586447e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2375032</a>"},{"pid":"d6d8350264d78db4bb2e769a4143bccfd53d88e9","tid":2368200,"uid":304916,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:38:12.000Z","msg":"希望黎生唔洗出入油麻地"},{"pid":"3d403d27491b03e398afba431ffd9e078d3876e8","tid":2368200,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5043489fc2d69c42b9f9cd57dce29df140a7a0d3","tid":2368200,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"疫苗顧問專家委員會成員、中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌說，委員會下星期一將會討論德國BioNTech與上海復星合作的新型肺炎疫苗，相信2月底開始為市民接種的機會高。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌出席一個電台節目後說，前日才收到藥廠提供的資料，這兩天會檢視資料，疫苗委員會下星期一將開會討論。對於挪威最近有至少23人接種BioNTech疫苗後死亡，他說，相關資料是從傳媒得知，如果藥廠提供的數據未有涵蓋有關事件，委員會會向藥廠索取補充資料。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570736-20210116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570736-20210116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=b910ad59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570736-20210116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fb23861b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570736-20210116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1a9e8f9160dc7ee1b8d5ba5335df45c46bf9fde6","tid":2368200,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c508a73851b7d02dcea03b012741cae891592f","tid":2368200,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1545f7db390d8fd29030288651d99a8f6c6c8cad","tid":2368200,"uid":25260,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"好彩黎生搭港島線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9c9bf7280ebc81fbaf6fac8d4d8c14a3dfd27f","tid":2368200,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"認左deep state card game<br />\nCNC既專家 行暴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7023079cfcff0e652eadda2bc478e4828ee72e","tid":2368200,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1545f7db390d8fd29030288651d99a8f6c6c8cad","tid":2368200,"uid":25260,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"好彩黎生搭港島線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ad12fe472e20448b0ebd837afe1ec2efd9fc88","tid":2368200,"uid":22902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T03:56:20.000Z","msg":"之前半山爆得勁又唔禁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkg